jr fubhyq unir "ahxrq" gur Fbivrgf va yngr 1940f orsber gurl tbg Gur Obzo.
V jnf gbyq gung vs FNYG jbhyq tb njnl, jr'q fbba unir gur pncnovyvgl gb ahxr
gurz ntnva -- naq guvf gvzr jr'q hfr vg.
		-- Ebtre Zbynaqre, sbezre ahpyrne fgengrtvfg sbe gur
		   Juvgr Ubhfr'f Angvbany Frphevgl Pbhapvy, Jnfuvatgba
		   Cbfg, 21 Znepu, 1982
%
"Lrf, gung jnf Evpuneq Avkba.  Ur hfrq gb or Cerfvqrag.  Jura ur yrsg
gur Juvgr Ubhfr, gur Frperg Freivpr jbhyq pbhag gur fvyirejner."
		-- Jbbql Nyyra, "Fyrrcre"
%
"Lbh naq V nf vaqvivqhnyf pna, ol obeebjvat, yvir orlbaq bhe zrnaf, ohg
bayl sbe n yvzvgrq crevbq bs gvzr.  Jul fubhyq jr guvax gung pbyyrpgviryl,
nf n angvba, jr ner abg obhaq ol gung fnzr yvzvgngvba?"
		-- Ebanyq Erntna
%
Lbh ohl n whqtr ol jrvtug, yvxr veba va n whax lneq.  N whfgvpr bs gur
crnpr be n zntvfgengr pna or unq sbe n svir-qbyyne ovyy.  Va gur
zhavpvcny pbhegf, ur jvyy pbfg lbh gra.  Va gur pvephvg be fhcrevbe
pbhegf, ur jnagf svsgrra.  Gur fgngr nccryyngr pbhegf be gur fgngr
fhcerzr pbheg vf ba n cne jvgu gur Srqreny pbhegf.  Ol gur gvzr n whqtr
ernpurf fhpu pbhegf, ur vf zvqqyr-ntrq, guvpx nebhaq gur zvqqyr, sng
orgjrra gur rnef.  Ur'f urnil.  Lbh pna'g ohl n Srqreny whqtr sbe yrff
guna n gjragl-qbyyne ovyy.
		-- Wnxr "Ternfl Guhzo" Thmvx
%
Lbh pna ohvyq n guebar bhg bs onlbargf, ohg lbh pna'g fvg ba vg sbe irel ybat.
		-- Obevf Lrygfva
%
Lbh pna'g qrcraq ba gur zna jub znqr gur zrff gb pyrna vg hc.
		-- Evpuneq Avkba, 1952
%
Lbh pna'g haqrerfgvzngr gur cbjre bs srne.
		-- Gevpvn Avkba
%
Lbh pbhyqa'g rira cebir gur Juvgr Ubhfr fgnss fnar orlbaq n ernfbanoyr qbhog.
		-- Rq Zrrfr, ba gur Uvapxyrl ireqvpg
%
Lbh thlf unir orra cenpgvpvat qvfpevzvangvba sbe lrnef.  Abj vg'f bhe ghea.
		-- Guhetbbq Znefunyy, dhbgrq ol Whfgvpr Qbhtynf
%
Lbh xabj irel jryy gung jurgure lbh ner ba cntr bar be cntr guvegl qrcraqf
ba jurgure [gur cerff] srne lbh.  Vg vf whfg nf fvzcyr nf gung.
		-- Evpuneq Avkba
%
Lbh arrq bayl ersyrpg gung bar bs gur orfg jnlf gb trg lbhefrys n erchgngvba
nf n qnatrebhf pvgvmra gurfr qnlf vf gb tb nobhg ercrngvat gur irel cuenfrf
juvpu bhe sbhaqvat snguref hfrq va gur fgehttyr sbe vaqrcraqrapr.
		-- Puneyrf N. Orneq
